            <item>
            <title><![CDATA[如果我就阿富汗局勢採訪習近平……]]></title>
            <link><![CDATA[https://cn.nytimes.com/opinion/20210820/afghanistan-us-taliban/zh-hant/?utm_source=RSS]]></link>
            <description><![CDATA[有關阿富汗事態發展，我最渴望採訪這三個人：前總統強生、中國主席習近平和阿富汗最後一位國王查希爾。本文是我想像中的採訪內容。<p><img src='https://static01.nyt.com/images/2021/08/19/opinion/19friedman-new-lead/merlin_107406217_378b2066-1224-47c3-9c99-81d827055573-articleLarge.jpg' alt=' Andrew Quilty for The New York Times'/></p>                    <p style='text-align: right; color: gray; font-size: 11px!important; line-height: 10px;'>Andrew Quilty for The New York Times</p>                    <p style='text-align: left; color: gray; font-size: 11px!important; line-height: 10px;'></p>                    ]]></description>
